                The bus wheezed to a stop, depositing Luffy, Usopp, and Nami near a weathered, fish-shaped building perched precariously over the churning sea. Waves crashed below, sending salty spray into the air. This was the Baratie Bistro, famed 'Echo Isle'. The air itself seemed thick with untold tales and the mouth-watering aroma of cooking.
            </p>
            <p><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50/FF0000/FFFFFF?text=L" alt="Luffy Icon" class="character-icon"><span class="luffy-dialogue">Shishishi! Smells like adventure... and MEAT!</span></p>
