            <p><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50/FFA500/FFFFFF?text=N" alt="Nami Icon" class="character-icon">"Alright, Luffy. Remember the plan. We find this 'Sanji' chef, see if his food *really* inspires stories, and maybe get a free meal if Usopp's 'legendary hero' tales work."</p>
            <p><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50/FFFF00/000000?text=U" alt="Usopp Icon" class="character-icon">"Leave it to Captain Usopp! They'll be feeding us like kings after they hear of my daring exploits!" *He puffs out his chest, nervously glancing at the imposing restaurant.*</p>
