            <h2>Chaos in the Kitchen</h2>
            <p class="narrative">
                Luffy didn't wait, bursting through the doors with a yell. <span class="luffy-dialogue">"FOOD! STORIES! HELLO!"</span> The inside was bustling, a chaotic symphony of clanging pans, shouting chefs, and diners laughing. Presiding over it all from a high stool near the kitchen was a stern-looking man with a braided blonde moustache and a prosthetic leg – Zeff. But before anyone could react to Luffy's entrance, a commotion erupted from the kitchen.
            </p>
            <p class="narrative">
                A figure in a chef's uniform, blond hair obscuring one eye, a cigarette dangling from his lips, sent a rude customer flying with a precise, powerful kick. "Get out! Never waste food in front of me, you scum!" he yelled, his voice smooth but laced with fury. Dishes crashed. Nami groaned. Usopp hid behind Luffy.
            </p>
            <div class="character-intro">
                <strong><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50/0000FF/FFFFFF?text=S" alt="Sanji Icon" class="character-icon">Character Introduced: Sanji</strong> - A passionate, fiery chef working at the Baratie. Reveres food and women, detests waste. His kicks are legendary amongst the staff.
