             <h2>Audience with the Owner</h2>
             <p class="narrative">Nami steered them towards the imposing Head Chef Zeff. "Excuse me, Mr. Zeff? We heard this place inspires great stories..." Zeff eyed them skeptically. "Stories, eh? This is a restaurant, girlie. We serve food, not fairy tales." Suddenly, Sanji kicked a customer out. Zeff sighed. "That damn eggplant..." Luffy immediately ran towards Sanji. <span class="luffy-dialogue">"Awesome kick! Are you Sanji?"</span> The scene converges similarly to `scene3_approachSanji`.</p>
