             <p class="narrative">They slipped inside amidst the chaos of the ejected customer. They saw Sanji arguing with Zeff, the tension palpable. Before they could decide who to approach, the Critique Pirates made their entrance. "Well, well. The infamous Baratie Bistro..." The atmosphere shifted instantly.</p>
