         <div class="scene hidden" id="scene4_confrontation">
             <h2>Critique Pirates Attack!</h2>
             <p class="narrative">Fullbody, leader of the Critique Pirates, sneered. "Your 'passionate' cooking, your 'emotional' stories... it's all unrefined dribble. We're here to impose some *standards*." His crew started heckling the diners and staff, trying to disrupt the atmosphere.</p>
             <p class="narrative">Sanji stepped forward, fists clenched (ready for kicking). "You talkin' about food? Or the old man's heart? Either way, you're outta line." Zeff glared, his peg leg tapping ominously.</p>
             <p><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50/FF0000/FFFFFF?text=L" alt="Luffy Icon" class="character-icon"><span class="luffy-dialogue">Hey! Leave them alone! Stories and food are best when they come from the heart! Shishishi!</span></p>
             <p class="narrative">Fullbody laughed mockingly. "Heart? How utterly... sentimental. Prove it, street urchin."</p>
             <div class="action">
                 <button onclick="showScene('scene5_luffyStory')">Luffy tells a story fueled by the Baratie's energy.</button>
